import { BrowserRouter as Router, Link } from "react-router-dom";
import styled from "styled-components";
import {
  NavigationBar,
  Container,
  Navlogo,
  NavBox,
  NavLogoText,
  NavBrand,
  NavItems,
  NavItem,
  NavItemLink,
  keyframes,
} from "./styles";

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <NavigationBar>
      <Container>
        <Navlogo>
          <NavBox>
            <NavLogoText>
              <Router>
                <NavBrand to="/">StarWars</NavBrand>
              </Router>
            </NavLogoText>
          </NavBox>
        </Navlogo>

        <NavItems>
          <NavItem>
            <Router>
              <NavItemLink exact path="/">
                Home
              </NavItemLink>
            </Router>
          </NavItem>
        </NavItems>
      </Container>
    </NavigationBar>
  );
};

export default Navbar;
